Join Jung Kook’s #SevenDaysAWeek challenge to win a chance to be in the ‘Seven (feat. Latto)’ compilation video.

Submission Link : bit.ly/3DuZx2d

*Submission period: July 14th 01:00 AM ~ July 24th 11:00 AM (Eastern Time)
*This event may be changed or canceled due to unforeseen circumstances of BIGHIT MUSIC and TikTok.
